title: Anastasia - Mi Milas | Αναστασία - Μη Μιλάς (Official Music Video)
description: Anastasia - Mi Milas | Αναστασία - Μη ΜιλάςBuy/Stream it here: https://Anastasia.lnk.to/MiMilasSubscribe: https://bit.ly/3qIX3YtΣτιχοι-Μουσικη: Γιώργος ΚαλογεράκοςΠαραγωγή-Ενορχήστρωση: Γιώργος Καλογεράκος - Νίκος ΧωρίτοςΠνευστά: Αποστολής Μαλλιάς Κιθάρα: Δημήτρης ΧατζηλαζαρίδηςRecorded mixed & mastered @ 718 Studios by Γιώργος Καλογεράκος - Νίκος ΧωρίτοςExecutive producer: Mike Stathakis____________________________________________Director: BodegaScript: Alexandros KostelidisProduction Manager: Dimitris Thomaidis (Undertube)Steadicam : Stefanos Knapp 1st AC : Arsinoi Pilou Grip : Kostas Stratis Electritian : Thororis KoutsoukanidisColorist: Andrei CordeevChoreography: Aria SkokouStyling: Spyros NathanailMake Up: GingerbreadHair: Spyridon Liapis Art Direction: Tzella Christopoulou, Natalia FragkathoulaScript Explanation: Anastasis KostelidisDirectors Note:Ο έρωτας είναι ένα συναίσθημα μοναδικό. Κάποιοι λένε πως είναι ο λόγος που ενσαρκώνεσαι και συνεχίζεις να διψάς για ζωή μέχρι και την τελευταία σου αναπνοή. Ο έρωτας δίνει ζωή αλλά κάποιες φορές εξαιτίας του, η ζωή σου θα μπει σε πιο σκοτεινά μονοπάτια. Θα νιώσεις την ανάγκη να βιώσεις το συναίσθημα του έρωτα, να μοιραστείς όλα αυτά που έχεις να δώσεις στο πρόσωπο που αγαπάς αλλά αυτή σου η ανάγκη θα βρει διέξοδο στο λάθος πρόσωπο. Εσύ θα έχεις την ανάγκη να μοιραστείς το κρασί του έρωτα που σε μεθάει αλλά το ποτήρι που διάλεξες να χύσεις μέσα το απόσταγμα της ψυχής σου φαντάζει ρηχό για να χωρέσει άλλα αυτά που έχεις μέσα σου να δώσεις. Θα προσπαθείς να μεταδώσεις την μέθη που νιώθεις αλλά αν το πρόσωπο που ερωτεύτηκες δεν θέλει να μοιραστεί το κρασί του έρωτα σου δεν θα μπορέσει να μεθύσει μαζί σου.Τότε θα νιώσεις να πνίγεσαι. Όλα αυτά που ήθελες να σας δένουν σαν ζευγάρι να γίνονται θηλιά σφιχτή γύρω από τον λαιμό σου. Ο έρωτας έγινε κουβάρι χωρίς να βρίσκεις την άκρη του και όσα έχτιζαν οι προσδοκίες σου έγιναν άμμος μέσα σε μία στιγμή. Όλα μοιάζουν απρόσωπα, η κατάσταση είναι τεταμένη, τα όρια σου έχουν φτάσει στο κόκκινο. Με λίγα λόγια ο δεσμός έγινε δεσμά. Κάνεις βήματα πίσω για να μην πέσεις από το χείλος του γκρεμού αλλά μέχρι πότε θα υποχωρείς? Η ζωή σου πρέπει να προχωρήσει, για αυτό μην φοβάσαι να πέσεις. Είναι ο μόνος τρόπος να σηκωθείς. Για να αντικρίσεις το φως της λύτρωσης θα πρέπει τα μάτια σου να συνηθίσουν στο σκοτάδι, θα πρέπει να βυθιστείς βαθιά μέσα σου και να γνωρίσεις τον άγνωστο σου εαυτό που έκρυβες στα έγκατα της ψυχής σου. Τότε θα νιώσεις ολόκληρος, τότε θα αρχίσεις να αναδύεσαι, όταν πια θα έχεις καταλάβει πως το άλλο σου μισό δεν βρίσκεται κάπου μακριά σου αλλά βαθιά μέσα σου. Εσύ έχεις ότι χρειάζεσαι, εσύ είσαι και το κρασί και το ποτήρι. Μην φοβηθείς να πέσεις, μην φοβηθείς να βυθιστείς. ____________________________________________Follow Anastasia on Social Media:Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/imanastasia_official/TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@imanastasia_officialFollow Golden Records on Social Media:Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/goldenrecords.gr/MINOS EMI - A Universal Music CompanyFacebook: http://bit.ly/MinosEmiFacebookInstagram: http://bit.ly/InstagramMinosEMI_YouTube Channel: http://bit.ly/MinosEmiYouTubeTikTok: https://vm.tiktok.com/KCvsRt/#Anastasia #MiMilas #GoldenRecords

title: I played around with a brand new silhouette and fabric and let's just say... I'm obsessed 👗 #fashion
description: Shop the Superdress https://bit.ly/3oq3kJDI truly believe that women’s clothing has to be designed in a way that moves WITH our bodies, not against it. I’m sick of dresses that restrict me! Like can’t I pick up something I dropped without worrying if my underwear is showing? Can’t I not have to cross my legs bc I’m afraid of someone is going to look up my skirt? I’m tired of it. I feel like I’ve got work to do outside the activewear space too if I’m going to make a real change in women’s clothing…Anyway, I want to share with you my latest @popflexactive workout dress design…I call this my ✨Superdress✨!I am playing with a brand new silhouette and fabric, and I’m loooove how sleek it turned out. Here’s what’s up:✔️ anti-🐫 shorts with no front seam✔️ pockets cuz duh✔️ stretchy lightweight fabric bc breathing and eating are v important✔️ thick, adjustable straps bc ✨comfort✨ and all our torsos are diff✔️ square neckline bc Bridgerton boobs obvs✔️ waist snatching panel cuz always✔️ slit bc it’s cute but also helps with leg movement✔️ longer skirt in the back for booty coverage✔️XXS-3XI’m trying a new pattern that’s a bit less twirly so that it gives more of a simplistic elegance. I love the sleek lines so much.I’m 5’5”, normally a small, wearing an XS HOWEVER I think you should get your normal size. I am very very particular when it comes to dresses. I size down in dresses for all brands bc I like the extra snatch it gives my waist and the extra lift it gives my boobs, but I think you’ll be safer in your normal size! Also one more thing! If you plan on getting black, size up from your normal size! The black dye made the fabric a tad less stretchy so you’ll want to account for that.The Superdress is on popflexactive.com @popflexactive in 4 colors! Which is your fave?♥️Cassey

title: Starship Flight Test
description: Starship gave us quite a show during today’s first flight test of a fully integrated Starship and Super Heavy rocket from Starbase in Texas.  At 8:33 a.m. CT, Starship successfully lifted off from the orbital launch pad for the first time. The vehicle cleared the pad and beach as Starship climbed to an apogee of ~39 km over the Gulf of Mexico – the highest of any Starship to-date. The vehicle experienced multiple engines out during the flight test, lost altitude, and began to tumble. The flight termination system was commanded on both the booster and ship. As is standard procedure, the pad and surrounding area was cleared well in advance of the test, and we expect the road and beach near the pad to remain closed until tomorrow.With a test like this, success comes from what we learn, and we learned a tremendous amount about the vehicle and ground systems today that will help us improve on future flights of Starship. Thank you to our customers, Cameron County, and the wider community for the continued support and encouragement. And congratulations to the entire SpaceX team on an exciting first flight test of Starship!

title: Gülcemal 2. Bölüm
description: Gülcemal 2. Bölüm (13 Nisan 2023)Gülcemal 3. Bölümü İzlemek İçin: https://youtu.be/pUhjm2SJrWMGülcemal Her Perşembe 20.00'de FOX'ta!Gülcemal 2. Bölüm Özeti:Gülcemal babasını bırakmak için Deva’ya bir teklifte bulunur. Halil İbrahim’i serbest bırakmak karşılığında Deva’nın onunla kalmasını istemektedir. Köşeye sıkışan Deva Gülcemal’in teklifini kabul etmek zorunda kalır. Bu sırada İpek Deva’yı kurtarmak için Zafer’den yardım ister ancak Zafer’in bambaşka planları vardır. Gülcemal’i hiç beklemediği bir yerden vurmak istemektedir. Deva ise hiç tanımadığı Gülcemal’in evindeki tutsaklıktan kurtulmak için kendi canını tehlikeye atar.Annesinin küçükken terk edip karanlık bir canavara dönüştürdüğü Gülcemal (Murat Ünalmış) ile güzeller güzeli Deva'nın (Melis Sezen) nefretle başlayıp giderek ateş, tutku ve fırtınanın girdabına savrulan aşkını konu alıyor... Gülcemal'in annesiyle olan savaşında, hiç hesapta olmayan aşk mı yoksa yıllardır güttüğü kin mi galip gelecektir? Bedellerle dolu bu yolda Gülcemal, gaddar bir avcıyken açık bir ava mı dönüşecektir? Peki Deva?
